{"tid":278670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★會活動的工具！馬鞍山綫唔准員工食早餐 ！員工斥：黑心企業","createTime":"2017-06-10T15:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T11:36:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53e28e22c1242271d8e2249cb810b9382760836b","tid":278670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"港鐵馬鞍山綫主管日前向前員工發出指示，禁止他們在上午7時後食早餐，違規者會被發警告信。有員工批評新政策不人道，擔心其他綫路亦會陸續實施新指示，要求公司撤回新政策。<br />\n<br />\n有不願透露姓名的馬鐵綫員工透露，最近有馬鞍山站、恆安站及烏溪沙站的員工接獲高層電郵通知，指令所有當值員工在上午7時後不准吃早餐，違規者會被發警告信，估計受影響的約有5、60人。<br />\n<br />\n有員工稱，各站員工上班時間各有不同，部份人清晨5時已當值，故難免會在當值時間吃早餐，「一般都係輪流食，有時會叫外賣響休息室食，總之一定有人當緊更，一直行之有效。」不過，該三站主管日前突然發電郵公佈有關食早餐的新規定，「好似最初話直情唔畀食，話係高層指示，後來就改為7點後唔畀食，仲話公司合約根本冇規定有食早餐時間，如果違規就出warning（警告信）。」<br />\n<br />\n他批評此新政策變相「逼人唔准食早餐」，因7時前很多店舖仍未營業，「未必買到早餐食，唔少人怕收warning，寧願捱到中午先食。」他批評此指令根本不人道，並已實行了數天，不少人敢怒不敢言，「成日話良心企業，根本就係黑心企業。」有員工更擔心政策會「火燒連環船」蔓延至其他綫路。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170610&amp;guid=56810684&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170610%26guid%3D56810684%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=wBcafSBMJWD7cDcEYs37IACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=9e479699\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170610%26guid%3D56810684%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=48557ace\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170610&amp;guid=56810684&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"edfc456e9fe36d1d6357f3d15c7882c25f853415","tid":278670,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://randomaunt.files.wordpress.com/2015/05/slave-beating.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frandomaunt.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F05%2Fslave-beating.png&h=0397fde4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef01c5a1cb1f55da44e70f8f778ae3ebe8c05ec1","tid":278670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:46:05.000Z","msg":"更擔心政策會「火燒連環船」蔓延至其他綫路。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8010bc6d4007a5e3f7131b6185179662daa0107","tid":278670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"蓋老母勿入"},{"pid":"17728e38ed28026a815b76d31ac0205584ff9c0f","tid":278670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"返工？不了！"},{"pid":"2fecb9ba16c73eaa759476ef25772dd907a5ecc0","tid":278670,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:48:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb3e014c59a9a3b097d9411b2bc2307c29fd7de6","tid":278670,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:48:06.000Z","msg":"不嬲朝早自己煮完嘢食先出門口"},{"pid":"fcea8a8dce9198d756e4780016b2c355ae2afefa","tid":278670,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:48:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"856c642e1327ed852f0f3eb1e6bceeabd393a4f0","tid":278670,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"出面啲公司快啲出memo唔准員工食早餐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ecf7a5d5c29dcc73215c8e42cfb290085405d4","tid":278670,"uid":54779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:53:07.000Z","msg":"抵啦 幫地鐵打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b99de7281e00f3e73aa074ed833585a9e712407","tid":278670,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislik